column5: Please excuse the formatting, not sure how to fix it.

Terrifying, every time. I have had them daily for over 2 years, multiple times a day , but when you're having one it is like the first time , every time. I hate trying to explain why I'm having a panic attack , most of the time I have no idea , and other times it's exhausting to explain why . Nice to know I'm not alone in this .
